 nervusAVR is a collection of optimized utilities I use for my AVR projects
 
 Supports the following chips:
	- ATMega32U4
 
 Supports following devices:
	- HD44780 LCD display
	- DS18B20 Programmable Resolution 1-Wire Digital Thermometer 

